Product Description
Edward Scissorhands is an artificial boy created by an inventor in the classic movie of the same name. The Women's Miss Edward Scissorhands Sexy Costume is a twist on that character. The costume comes with a female dress version of Edward Scissorhands' outfit. It's short and black with faux leather details. It also comes with a black choker, a black faux leather belt, a wild black wig, and glovelettes. It also comes, of course, with Edward Scissorhands most prominent and unusual feature: scissors for hands. These gloves make you look like you have scissors instead of fingers. Because Edward had no fingers, only sharp scissors, his clothing was shredded. The dress in this costume looks shredded, and you can purchase ripped stockings from us as well. We also sell boots that would be perfect for this costume. Wear this sexy and unusual costume to any Halloween party and turn some heads.
